公平性、银行系统支持等问题。各个城市、各个分行不一样，很多客户的情况不一样，都要考虑到。”彭家文指出，总体来看，招商银行会在央行的指导下按照市场化、法制化的原则稳妥地推进实施。 据了解，招行已从乐观情景、中性情景和不利三种情景对存量房贷利率下行进行了测算。从测算的结果来看，影响总体可控。 彭家文指出，存量房贷利率的调整也有其正面的影响。存量房贷利率下调的背景是因为提前还贷的量比较大。随着存量房贷利率的下调，整个住房贷款的提前还贷的因素会有一定程度的消化，反过来会带来房贷量的增长。同时，随着存量房贷利率下调，一定程度上会增强我们客户的黏度，会让银行对客户的经营进一步加深，从而对零售业务的增长有利。"},"attached_info":"Cj8Ir8nB7c6JsfJgEAMaCDk5OTgwOTU1ILXHtacGMAA4hgNAHHIJNjE5NjU0Mzk0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"4.6 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-bdab720c0c77017a2c52de846739cbd4_xl.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"29_1693360077.543283","card_id":"Q_614443320","target":{"id":614443320,"title":"日常生活中经常熬夜，有哪些能在熬夜后快速恢复的好物？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/614443320","type":"question","created":1690531772,"answer_count":30,"follower_count":87,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[5797,31071,2885934,2886966,2887257],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj4Ir8nB7c6JsfJgEAMaCDk4ODIzMjE3ILzvjaYGMAA4V0Adcgk2MTQ0NDMzMjB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"4.6 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-7081bc92765e211739eadf51d0108bb6_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"30_1693360077.543970","card_id":"Q_619415252","target":{"id":619415252,"title":"同事休产假我接替她组长的工作，结果她回来领导要我继续当组长，我自己很犹豫怎么办?","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/619415252","type":"question","created":1693140032,"answer_count":76,"follower_count":156,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[17420,98826,127198],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8Ir8nB7c6JsfJgEAMaCDk5OT